# amnesia-fix.tape — vhs script for the amnesia-fix demo GIF.

Output "demos/amnesia-fix.gif"

Set Theme "GitHub Dark"
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1080
Set Height 780
Set Padding 24
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set Framerate 24

Hide
Type "clear && bash demos/scenario-amnesia-fix.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 17s
